      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/devaH/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/saMhitA/vishvAsa-prastutiH/10/151_shraddhA/&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h2&gt;१५१ श्रद्धा-सूक्तम् ...{Loading}...&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;+++(तैत्तिरीयब्राह्मणे पादशो विभागः। ऋग्वेदे त्व् अर्धशो यथासाधारणम्।)+++&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled=&#34;&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/devaH/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/saMhitA/mUlam/10/151/01_shraddhayAgniH_samidhyate.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;०१ श्रद्धयाग्निः समिध्यते ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;श्र॒द्धया॒ ऽग्निस् समि॑ध्यते । श्र॒द्धया॑ विन्दते ह॒विः ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;श्र॒द्धां भग॑स्य मू॒र्धनि॑ । वच॒साऽऽवे॑दयामसि ।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled=&#34;&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/devaH/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/saMhitA/mUlam/10/151/02_priyaM_shraddhe.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;०२ प्रियं श्रद्धे ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;प्रि॒य२ꣳ श्र॑द्धे॒ दद॑तः । प्रि॒य२ꣳ श्र॑द्धे॒ दिदा॑सतः ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;प्रि॒यं भो॒जेषु॒ यज्व॑सु। इ॒दं म॑ उदि॒तङ् कृ॑धि ।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;js_include&#34; includetitle=&#34;false&#34; newlevelforh1=&#34;2&#34; unfilled=&#34;&#34; url=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/devaH/vedAH_Rk/shAkalam/saMhitA/mUlam/10/151/03_yathA_devA.md&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;&lt;h4&gt;०३ यथा देवा ...{Loading}...&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;यथा॑ दे॒वा असु॑रेषु । श्र॒द्धाम् उ॒ग्रेषु॑ चक्रि॒रे ।&lt;br&gt;&#xA;ए॒वं भो॒जेषु॒ यज्व॑सु । अ॒स्माक॑म् उदि॒तङ् कृ॑धि ।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
